{"tid":856683,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人拍拖成日都好冇安全感","createTime":"2018-10-10T17:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T17:34:07.000Z","uid":202914,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5395b2a46e9b39de5e57a01757d07534d7cf8bea","tid":856683,"uid":202914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"其實男朋友對我好好<br />\n平日工作攰同放假都會陪我<br />\n我有心事會開解我<br />\n做每樣嘢都好照顧我感受<br />\n超級錫我<br />\n但我成日覺得自己條件差配唔上佢 <br />\n好驚佢會唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好冇安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我真係好愛你架男朋友</span></span>"},{"pid":"98a04d4942e2e6b9127dbf2bf6618ebb24f083b9","tid":856683,"uid":208726,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da144c9e61a07a49cb11edfaf30376f7bd3072df","tid":856683,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"男朋友係咪好靚仔"},{"pid":"6e78eeea0c8ddd0dd6e5b04f8f01c24de060648d","tid":856683,"uid":202914,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"98a04d4942e2e6b9127dbf2bf6618ebb24f083b9","tid":856683,"uid":208726,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798cf5b20f3cd7fdad9f13716b0579ea40a31ac2","tid":856683,"uid":202914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da144c9e61a07a49cb11edfaf30376f7bd3072df","tid":856683,"uid":199162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"男朋友係咪好靚仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:12:01.000Z","msg":"正常樣"},{"pid":"832872c93ef319a0a2acaae048606a6da8b072c9","tid":856683,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1154d377d1dbfdae3d0b8abe6a88f629ab25f815","tid":856683,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:14:15.000Z","msg":"放過你條仔啦<br />\n男人青春有限"},{"pid":"07cccf24c92ed76affd5b71281f76010a4457ecf","tid":856683,"uid":202914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"832872c93ef319a0a2acaae048606a6da8b072c9","tid":856683,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e78eeea0c8ddd0dd6e5b04f8f01c24de060648d","tid":856683,"uid":202914,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"98a04d4942e2e6b9127dbf2bf6618ebb24f083b9","tid":856683,"uid":208726,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"暫時未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b06d8a7db31485dc871487ad320b774e00c3b55","tid":856683,"uid":56772,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"我都好多時會無安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然每晚都同男朋友傾電話<br />\n但傾親佢都係玩緊電話<br />\n永遠都好似係我講我嘅生活事而佢就淨係聽話者可能無聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時都會同佢講下自己嘅諗法<br />\n但佢接收完之後就會好似講下笑咁耍走我<br />\n但又會講話淨係會得我一個<br />\n我之後都懶得再講落去了<br />\n佢就成日feel到我失落都唔理我<br />\n覺得我過一陣都會搵返佢(我又真係次次都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n不過其實每次都記咗喺心到<br />\n同埋佢份工又多女同事 D樣又唔差<br />\n搞到我有時都會好怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 平時咩都聽哂佢話 好少嘈交 樣中上 不過高大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d0607d0bd1e1bee99f9495bb263238d3d49cd8","tid":856683,"uid":88990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"與其用時間胡思亂想，<br />\n不如用時間學化妝、扮靚、穿搭、減肥⋯⋯<br />\n增值自己，自信心都高d"},{"pid":"1ee33c6f05bb9638bfb6847fcede417ab9629178","tid":856683,"uid":188150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"極缺乏安全感 成日擔心男朋友嫌棄我😭<br />\n好明你感受！所以我好努力想令自己拍得住佢"}]}